products.title: AMD Ryzen 3 3300X 4-Core, 8-Thread Unlocked Desktop Processor with Wraith Stealth Cooler
features: 3rd Gen AMD Ryzen processors are the world's most advanced in the desktop PC gaming segment
Can deliver smooth 100+ FPS performance in the world's most popular games, discrete graphics card required
4 cores and 8 processing threads, bundled with the quiet AMD Wraith Stealth cooler
4.3 GHz Max Boost, unlocked for overclocking, 18 MB of GameCache, DDR-3200 support
For the advanced Socket AM4 platform, can support PCIe 4.0 on X570 and B550 motherboards
products.description: With 4 cores and 8 processing threads for twice the multitasking capability, the advanced 3rd Gen Ryzen 3 3300X is the fastest Ryzen 3 processor for intense gaming when paired with a discrete graphics card.
